<p>26/11/17<br/>to see the moor covered also the bush near by huts etc  The Russian business seems rather rotten we do not know what to believe about the reports are so conflicting</p>
<p>27/11/17<br/>General Maud dead.  More snow this morning only a light fall.  rain during the day with a driving wind</p>
<p>28/11/17<br/>Rain again today  Letter from Mother dated 28/7/17.  first books from Jim Coombs through red cross.  War news good all round except Russia wanting peace so the German papers say Manofesto issued by Russian General to fight on.</p>
<p>29/11/17<br/>Miserable day slight rain all day.  Russian affair still the same  Germany will give</p>
